le OCD, so I can't play a game with 1.5-2 inches of the gameplay off the side of the visible monitor. Games shouldn't be released like this in 2015. I've tried all of the staff suggestions and none of them have provided a satisfactory screen/resolution or fixed the 1440 x 900 issue, which they haven't even agreed is a bug yet.Multiple complaints on their forums about resolutions and they release a bug fix patch neglecting the resolutions issues.For almost a month people complained about resolution incompatibilities and nothing was done. Poor service.Avoid until they a) fix the many bugs and b) offer some additional content. The 'remastered' features are not, I repeat not, worth buying this for.I no longer own the game, removed/refunded."
