s before, this game is a MUST!!! I really do love the combat and upgrading your survivors abilities. Using firearms creates a lot of noise but the sounds they make are realisitc. Even the voice acting isnt too bad, there are however, the same things they continually say which can get anoying.I could go on and on about this game but there are several other reviews that go into much detail of how fun this game is."
