76561198031885209,Recommended,329430,16424114,"Posted: 15 June, 2015",all,Prophet,"So what is this game?It's a zombie apocalypse open survival game.Enough said to be honest.Story: X/10So why a X instead of a number?Well, it might be because I really don't know which mission is the story, and there's basically no story at all at the same time where there is one. The game throws a x amount of missions at the player at roughly the same time.Gameplay: 8/10The gameplay is good, really good and addictive but it ha it's rough edges.The game starts with introducing the settlement mechaninc a settlement is a place where the survivors that you found live. For them to be able to live, they need food, medication and a place to sleep. Food and medication is able be found within the world itself, while you need to build a place for your survivors to sleep. Each settlement has it's own selected areas where you can choice what you want to build. If you want to have a survivor with you, well you gonna want to do a lot of side missions so you can rise your morale in your settlement, a low morale will make people leave your settlement.Looting is a big mechanic in the game, you do it like 80% of the time. It works but it's kinda weird. For some reason rushing a looting process makes more sound than shooting a zombie with a shotgun.The ""fighting"" mechanic works more or less. Shooting feels good but actually fighting feels awkward most of the time.You need to earn fame before you can take a weapon from your settlemet, yes you can find a gun and ammo in the world itself.Music: 7/10It's nothing special, but it's quite impressive when you can hear a gun shot in the distance.AI: 5/10This is the ""best"" thing in the game. If I could earn steam money for every time where an AI used their gun instead of melee a zombie. Sometimes they shoot when a zombie is not aggresive, and making them and every zombie within 20 feet aggresive on you.Total score: 7/10It might seem like I'm hating on the game, and in a way that's true. The game is really good, but it has it's rough edges. I'm on a ""mission"" to find the perfect survival game and this game is on the top three on my list. It's funny and challenging at the same time. It could have been so much better if they had fixed some of the things that have told you about in this review."
