ng, empathetic solution's liquefaction - seeping heartward, salting now-ephemeral human wounds.You stop.Strike out!Sweep the cliffs, sweep the shallows for some poultice, for some penitent panacea - an herb, a vial, a bottle, a philosophy - anything...everything...something.Each footstep first thundered, in passion, now's a noose, each footstep strung in heart sinew, stumble's pounds to bear, whimpers come in volley, tears trailing from trebuchets, splashing hard around the ears.Til each wail's a windlass - descending downwards with a knell...cranial crevasses calmly creeping, knowing naught is all's been found.This is your world, is your misery, is your mercy shot against your once-loved friend. This is horror...is honor...is triumph...is survival...is your mind's eye into this world."
