,Recommended,329430,32077165,Posted: 30 May,all,♂ Maiye✨,"For those wanting to buy this game, warning, because when playing in fullscreen (for me anyway) the game was locked at 24fps even though I know I can run far above 60. The way I got around this was going to Properties, Set Launch Options and putting in the following commands: -windowed -noborder   By doing this it bypasses the 24fps lock so that it plays at the framerate it should be at.Other than that and some other bugs this game is pretty damn good, if you can look past all of its faults."
